This led to 100-s of false registrations that flooded our system and mailboxes.   Therefore, we had no option but to disable registration through the Wiki. Users who want access to this Wiki can sent a request by email to the Wiki administration address: ro_wiki at astron dot nl.</description>     </item> </rdf:RDF>
